snippet.title: Bombing!! 2: A Graffiti Paradise - Official Gameplay Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Bombing!! 2: A Graffiti Paradise will be available on PC on June 27, 2023. Take a tour of the open world in this chill trailer for the creative sandbox game where the world is 100% paintable. Meet friendly characters, unlock new tools and paint your graffiti all over Graffiti Paradise.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
